column5: Small clips of me trying to trick a few small panfish. Try full screen for better quality, I don't know why some of my videos are not in landscape view. Any solutions? I was using my iPhone 4
man you are killing me with these videos.  good job though.  keep em coming its my only way to be close to ice fishing
Can't help you with the view young_one but looks like it was fun making those vids Thanks for sharing Leechman
Always enjoy the underwater vids, thanks for posting!
awww, no audio of your lure talking to the fish again?
Given the choice of some of the diluted fishing shows available to viewers today and watching an Aqua Vu screen, I would vote for the Aqua Vu.  I say bring on the 24 hour Aqua Vu channel.
